{"type":"message","id":"ef9a93c7","parentId":"0c58ba44","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:29:34.381Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_xg4r6mfe0xy9_1","toolName":"memory_get","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"text\": \"# 2026-04-22\\n\\n## Session Monitoring Setup\\n- User yêu cầu giám sát master session\\n- Đã setup cron job: `*/5 * * * *` chạy `monitor-session.sh` mỗi 5 phút\\n- Script check session status và alert qua Telegram nếu chết\\n- Log file: `memory/session-monitor.log`\\n\\n## SafeSight AI Project\\n- Hoàn thành specs cho s1-ppe-safety (SafeSight AI)\\n- Frontend demo đang chạy: https://glance-rain-falling-edges.trycloudflare.com\\n- Đã push lên GitLab: pet-connect2/s1-ppe-safety-monitoring (develop branch)\\n\",\n  \"path\": \"memory/2026-04-22.md\"\n}"}],"details":{"text":"# 2026-04-22\n\n## Session Monitoring Setup\n- User yêu cầu giám sát master session\n- Đã setup cron job: `*/5 * * * *` chạy `monitor-session.sh` mỗi 5 phút\n- Script check session status và alert qua Telegram nếu chết\n- Log file: `memory/session-monitor.log`\n\n## SafeSight AI Project\n- Hoàn thành specs cho s1-ppe-safety (SafeSight AI)\n- Frontend demo đang chạy: https://glance-rain-falling-edges.trycloudflare.com\n- Đã push lên GitLab: pet-connect2/s1-ppe-safety-monitoring (develop branch)\n","path":"memory/2026-04-22.md"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776835774375}}
{"type":"message","id":"a0729153","parentId":"ef9a93c7","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:29:41.416Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The memory doesn't show what happened with the Confluence pages. But from the exec messages in the system notification:\n- `swift-tr` created Confluence pages for \"AHV CMS Teacher - Đào tạo lái xe\" with sub-items\n\nThe user is saying they asked me to write based on a reference for the ahv-qlhv project, not copy it. This means I likely copied content from an existing document instead of writing original content inspired by a reference.\n\nI need to acknowledge this and ask what they want me to do differently. I should admit the mistake and offer to fix it.","thinkingSignature":"149788a8857f6b4380b80e00df459c149f23381579e4dfbdf694e2d1a0b17124"},{"type":"text","text":"\nXin lỗi, Khương. Mình đã copy nội dung từ tài liệu tham chiếu thay vì viết lại dựa trên ý tưởng từ nó.\n\nBạn muốn mình:\n1. **Xóa các trang Confluence** vừa tạo và viết lại nội dung độc original cho từng mục?\n2. **Giữ cấu trúc** nhưng viết lại nội dung theo phong cách khác?\n3. **Giữ nguyên** và chỉ sửa các phần bị copy?\n\nCho mình biết hướng bạn muốn nhé."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":262,"output":307,"cacheRead":14527,"cacheWrite":3091,"totalTokens":18187,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776835774383,"responseId":"06378fbfa152736fade483a13e69e5ba"}}
