{"type":"message","id":"7124f4bb","parentId":"54c5b371","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:55:34.823Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Khương đang hỏi tiến độ. Tôi đã tạo được 2 trang:\n1. Trang chính: 1. Tổng quan dự án (130744535)\n2. Trang con: 2. Nghiệp vụ & Sản phẩm (130810420)\n\nTôi đang tiếp tục tạo các trang khác. Để tôi tiếp tục tạo nhanh các trang còn lại.","thinkingSignature":"d6662eb6b144de55f5adebfb9e176ea15abfb6cd7cfef50f4c9bb4ba248fee20"},{"type":"text","text":"Đang tiến hành! Đã tạo được 2 trang, đang tiếp tục các trang còn lại:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n6wg3iohim6s_1","name":"confluence__create_page","arguments":{"title":"3. Kiến trúc hệ thống - System Architecture","space":"AHVTEACHER","body":"# 3. Kiến trúc hệ thống - System Architecture\n\n## 📋 Mục lục\n1. [Tổng quan kiến trúc](#tổng-quan-kiến-trúc)\n2. [Sơ đồ ngữ cảnh](#sơ-đồ-ngữ-cảnh)\n3. [Kiến trúc High-level](#kiến-trúc-high-level)\n4. [Luồng dữ liệu](#luồng-dữ-liệu)\n5. [Thiết kế Module](#thiết-kế-module)\n\n---\n\n## Tổng quan kiến trúc\n\nAHV CMS Teacher sử dụng kiến trúc **3-tier (Three-Layer Architecture)** kết hợp **Clean Architecture**:\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    PRESENTATION LAYER                    │\n│                   (React + Vite + TypeScript)            │\n│   ┌──────────┐ ┌──────────┐ ┌──────────┐ ┌──────────┐  │\n│   │ Dashboard│ │ Student  │ │ Course   │ │ Schedule │  │\n│   │   Page   │ │   Page   │ │   Page   │ │   Page   │  │\n│   └──────────┘ └──────────┘ └──────────┘ └──────────┘  │\n│   ┌──────────┐ ┌──────────┐ ┌──────────┐ ┌──────────┐  │\n│   │ Teacher  │ │ Finance  │ │  Report  │ │ Settings │  │\n│   │   Page   │ │   Page   │ │   Page   │ │   Page   │  │\n│   └──────────┘ └──────────┘ └──────────┘ └──────────┘  │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                           │\n                           ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                     API GATEWAY                          │\n│                   (Fastify + REST API)                   │\n│   ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n│   │              Authentication Middleware           │   │\n│   │                  (JWT + RBAC)                    │   │\n│   └─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n│   ┌────────┐ ┌────────┐ ┌────────┐ ┌────────┐          │\n│   │ Auth   │ │Student │ │Course  │ │Schedule│  ...     │\n│   │ Routes │ │ Routes │ │ Routes │ │ Routes │          │\n│   └────────┘ └────────┘ └────────┘ └────────┘          │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                           │\n                           ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                      SERVICE LAYER                       │\n│              (Business Logic + Validation)              │\n│   ┌────────────┐ ┌────────────┐ ┌────────────┐          │\n│   │  Student   │ │  Course    │ │  Schedule  │          │\n│   │  Service   │ │  Service   │ │  Service   │          │\n│   └────────────┘ └────────────┘ └────────────┘          │\n│   ┌────────────┐ ┌────────────┐ ┌────────────┐          │\n│   │  Teacher   │ │  Finance   │ │   Report   │          │\n│   │  Service   │ │  Service   │ │  Service   │          │\n│   └────────────┘ └────────────┘ └────────────┘          │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                           │\n                           ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    DATA ACCESS LAYER                      │\n│                  (MongoDB + Mongoose ODM)                │\n│   ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │\n│   │              Repository Pattern                  │   │\n│   └─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n│   ┌────────┐ ┌────────┐ ┌────────┐ ┌────────┐          │\n│   │Students│ │Courses │ │Schedule│ │Finance │  ...     │\n│   └────────┘ └────────┘ └────────┘ └────────┘          │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## Sơ đồ ngữ cảnh\n\n```\n┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                      AHV CMS TEACHER SYSTEM                       │\n│                                                                  │\n│    ┌─────────┐                              ┌─────────┐         │\n│    │  Admin │                              │ Teacher │         │\n│    └───┬────┘                              └───┬────┘         │\n│        │                                        │               │\n│        │ 3. CRUD Users                         │ 3. Manage     │\n│        │    Manage Roles                       │    Students   │\n│        │    System Config                      │    Courses    │\n│        │                                        │    Schedule   │\n│        ▼                                        ▼               │\n│    ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐       │\n│    │                                                     │       │\n│    │              WEB APPLICATION (CMS)                  │       │\n│    │                                                     │       │\n│    │  ┌───────────┐  ┌───────────┐  ┌───────────┐       │       │\n│    │  │ Dashboard │  │ Student   │  │ Schedule  │ ...   │       │\n│    │  │   Module  │  │  Module   │  │  Module   │       │       │\n│    │  └───────────┘  └───────────┘  └───────────┘       │       │\n│    │                                                     │       │\n│    └─────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────┘       │\n│                          │                                      │\n│    ┌─────────────────────┴───────────────────────────────┐      │\n│    │              BACKEND API (Fastify)                   │      │\n│    │                                                       │      │\n│    │  ┌──────────┐  ┌──────────┐  ┌──────────┐          │      │\n│    │  │  Auth    │  │ Business │  │  Report  │          │      │\n│    │  │  Module  │  │  Logic   │  │  Module  │          │      │\n│    │  └──────────┘  └──────────┘  └──────────┘          │      │\n│    └─────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────┘      │\n│                          │                                      │\n│    ┌─────────────────────┴───────────────────────────────┐      │\n│    │                   MONGODB                            │      │\n│    │   ┌─────────┐ ┌─────────┐ ┌─────────┐ ┌─────────┐   │      │\n│    │   │ Students│ │ Courses │ │Schedule │ │ Finance │   │      │\n│    │   └─────────┘ └─────────┘ └─────────┘ └─────────┘   │      │\n│    └────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘      │\n│                                                                  │\n└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## Kiến trúc High-level\n\n### 3.1. Frontend Architecture\n\n```\nsrc/\n├── api/                    # API clients\n│   ├── auth.ts            # Authentication API\n│   ├── student.api.ts     # Student API\n│   ├── course.api.ts      # Course API\n│   └── ...\n├── components/            # Reusable components\n│   ├── common/           # Button, Input, Modal, Table...\n│   ├── layout/           # Header, Sidebar, Footer\n│   └── charts/          # Chart components\n├── pages/                # Page components\n│   ├── dashboard/       # Dashboard page\n│   ├── students/        # Student management\n│   ├── courses/         # Course management\n│   └── ...\n├── hooks/               # Custom React hooks\n├── contexts/           # React contexts (Auth, Theme...)\n├── utils/             # Utility functions\n└── types/             # TypeScript types\n```\n\n### 3.2. Backend Architecture\n\n```\nsrc/\n├── controllers/        # Route handlers\n│   ├── auth.controller.ts\n│   ├── student.controller.ts\n│   └── ...\n├── services/          # Business logic\n│   ├── auth.service.ts\n│   ├── student.service.ts\n│   └── ...\n├── repositories/      # Data access (Repository pattern)\n│   ├── student.repository.ts\n│   └── ...\n├── models/            # Mongoose schemas\n│   ├── student.model.ts\n│   ├── course.model.ts\n│   └── ...\n├── middlewares/       # Express middlewares\n│   ├── auth.middleware.ts\n│   ├── error.middleware.ts\n│   └── ...\n├── routes/           # Route definitions\n├── validators/      # Request validation\n├── utils/           # Utility functions\n└── config/         # Configuration\n```\n\n### 3.3. Database Schema\n\n```\n┌─────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────┐\n│     User        │     │    Course       │     │    Student      │\n├─────────────────┤     ├─────────────────┤     ├─────────────────┤\n│ _id              │     │ _id              │     │ _id              │\n│ email            │     │ name             │     │ name             │\n│ password         │     │ code             │     │ cccd             │\n│ role             │     │ type (A1,B1...)  │     │ phone            │\n│ teacherInfo_id ──┼────▶│ startDate        │     │ address          │\n│ isActive         │     │ endDate          │     │ dateOfBirth      │\n└─────────────────┘     │ fee              │     │ courses[] ───────┼──┐\n                        │ status           │     └─────────────────┘  │\n                        │ students[]       │                          │\n                        └─────────────────┘                          │\n                               │                                     │\n                               │                                     │\n                        ┌──────┴──────┐                    ┌─────────┴────────┐\n                        │  Schedule  │                    │ CourseStudent   │\n                        ├────────────┤                    ├──────────────────┤\n                        │ _id         │                    │ course_id        │\n                        │ course_id   │                    │ student_id       │\n                        │ date        │                    │ enrolledDate     │\n                        │ shift       │                    │ progress         │\n                        │ teacher_id  │◀─────────          │ status           │\n                        │ room        │                    └──────────────────┘\n                        │ status      │\n                        └────────────┘\n\n┌─────────────────┐     ┌─────────────────┐\n│    Finance      │     │    Exam         │\n├─────────────────┤     ├─────────────────┤\n│ _id              │     │ _id              │\n│ type (in/out)    │     │ student_id       │\n│ amount           │     │ course_id        │\n│ description      │     │ type (theory/    │\n│ date             │     │   practical)     │\n│ category         │     │ score            │\n│ reference_id     │     │ examDate         │\n│ createdBy        │     │ passed           │\n└─────────────────┘     └─────────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## Luồng dữ liệu\n\n### Authentication Flow\n```\n┌────────┐     ┌────────┐     ┌─────────┐     ┌──────────┐\n│ Client │────▶│ Login  │────▶│ Verify  │────▶│JWT Token │\n│        │     │Request │     │ Password│     │Generated │\n└────────┘     └────────┘     └─────────┘     └──────────┘\n                                                    │\n                                                   ▼\n                                            ┌──────────┐\n                                            │ Store in │\n                                            │ Local    │\n                                            │ Storage  │\n                                            └──────────┘\n                                                    │\n                                                   ▼\n                                            ┌──────────┐\n                                            │Attach to │\n                                            │ subsequent│\n                                            │  Requests│\n                                            └──────────┘\n```\n\n### CRUD Operation Flow\n```\n┌────────┐     ┌────────┐     ┌──────────┐     ┌────────────┐\n│ Client │────▶│API     │────▶│ Validate │────▶│ Service    │\n│        │     │ Request│     │ Request  │     │ Logic      │\n└────────┘     └────────┘     └──────────┘     └────────────┘\n                                                    │\n                                                   ▼\n                                            ┌────────────┐\n                                            │Repository  │\n                                            │ (MongoDB)   │\n                                            └────────────┘\n                                                    │\n                                                   ▼\n                                            ┌────────────┐\n                                            │ Response   │\n                                            │ to Client  │\n                                            └────────────┘\n```\n\n---\n\n## Thiết kế Module\n\n### 4.1. Auth Module\n- **Chức năng**: Xác thực, phân quyền\n- **Endpoints**: `/auth/login`, `/auth/register`, `/auth/refresh`\n- **Dependencies**: User model\n\n### 4.2. Student Module\n- **Chức năng**: Quản lý học viên\n- **Endpoints**: CRUD, phân khóa học, cập nhật tiến độ\n- **Dependencies**: User, Course, Exam\n\n### 4.3. Course Module\n- **Chức năng**: Quản lý khóa học\n- **Endpoints**: CRUD, thêm/xóa học viên\n- **Dependencies**: Student, Schedule\n\n### 4.4. Schedule Module\n- **Chức năng**: Quản lý lịch học, lịch thi\n- **Endpoints**: CRUD, theo dõi điểm danh\n- **Dependencies**: Course, Teacher\n\n### 4.5. Finance Module\n- **Chức năng**: Quản lý thu chi\n- **Endpoints**: CRUD, báo cáo\n- **Dependencies**: Course\n\n### 4.6. Report Module\n- **Chức năng**: Tổng hợp dữ liệu, xuất báo cáo\n- **Endpoints**: Dashboard, charts, export\n- **Dependencies**: Tất cả modules\n\n---\n\n## 📅 Cập nhật\n\n| Ngày | Phiên bản | Thay đổi |\n|------|-----------|-----------|\n| 2026-04-22 | 1.0 | Tạo mới tài liệu |\n","parent_id":"130744535"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":3313,"cacheRead":27791,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31104,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776837286000,"responseId":"063795a74b49a90e000cf47a3788bff7"}}
{"type":"message","id":"881bb25c","parentId":"7124f4bb","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:55:36.203Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_n6wg3iohim6s_1","toolName":"confluence__create_page","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"id\":\"130777263\",\"title\":\"3. Kiến trúc hệ thống - System Architecture\",\"space\":\"AHVTEACHER\",\"url\":\"https://dtlx.atlassian.net/spaces/AHVTEACHER/pages/130777263/3.+Ki+n+tr+c+h+th+ng+-+System+Architecture\"}"}],"details":{"mcpServer":"confluence","mcpTool":"create_page"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776837336197}}
{"type":"message","id":"befadd2a","parentId":"881bb25c","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:56:27.374Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Tiếp tục tạo các trang khác. Đã có 3 trang rồi. Tiếp tục tạo:\n- 4. Tài liệu kỹ thuật\n- 5. API Documentation\n- 6. Database Documentation\n- 7. DevOps & Deployment\n- 8. Development Guideline\n- 9. Testing Documentation\n- 10. Operation & Maintenance\n\nLàm nhanh và gửi update liên tục cho Khương.","thinkingSignature":"f20ef6840d538b603988fb29142680429442849fa17755fe56d615b8a8bd4f03"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9k8av4to30rx_1","name":"confluence__create_page","arguments":{"title":"4. Tài liệu kỹ thuật - Technical Documentation","space":"AHVTEACHER","body":"# 4. Tài liệu kỹ thuật - Technical Documentation\n\n## 📋 Mục lục\n1. [Backend Documentation](#backend-documentation)\n2. [Frontend Documentation](#frontend-documentation)\n3. [Coding Conventions](#coding-conventions)\n4. [Error Handling Strategy](#error-handling-strategy)\n\n---\n\n## Backend Documentation\n\n### Công nghệ sử dụng\n\n| Technology | Version | Purpose |\n|------------|---------|---------|\n| **Node.js** | 20.x LTS | Runtime environment |\n| **Fastify** | 4.x | Web framework |\n| **TypeScript** | 5.x | Type safety |\n| **Mongoose** | 8.x | MongoDB ODM |\n| **MongoDB** | 7.x | Database |\n| **JWT** | - | Authentication |\n| **Zod** | - | Schema validation |\n\n### Cấu trúc thư mục\n\n```\nahv-dtlx-backend/\n├── src/\n│   ├── config/                 # Configuration\n│   │   ├── database.ts        # MongoDB connection\n│   │   ├── jwt.ts             # JWT config\n│   │   └── server.ts          # Server config\n│   │\n│   ├── controllers/           # Route handlers\n│   │   ├── auth.controller.ts\n│   │   ├── student.controller.ts\n│   │   ├── course.controller.ts\n│   │   ├── schedule.controller.ts\n│   │   ├── finance.controller.ts\n│   │   └── user.controller.ts\n│   │\n│   ├── services/              # Business logic\n│   │   ├── auth.service.ts\n│   │   ├── student.service.ts\n│   │   ├── course.service.ts\n│   │   ├── schedule.service.ts\n│   │   ├── finance.service.ts\n│   │   └── report.service.ts\n│   │\n│   ├── repositories/          # Data access layer\n│   │   ├── base.repository.ts\n│   │   ├── student.repository.ts\n│   │   ├── course.repository.ts\n│   │   └── ...\n│   │\n│   ├── models/               # Mongoose schemas\n│   │   ├── user.model.ts\n│   │   ├── student.model.ts\n│   │   ├── course.model.ts\n│   │   ├── schedule.model.ts\n│   │   └── finance.model.ts\n│   │\n│   ├── routes/               # Route definitions\n│   │   ├── index.ts\n│   │   ├── auth.routes.ts\n│   │   ├── student.routes.ts\n│   │   └── ...\n│   │\n│   ├── middlewares/          # Middlewares\n│   │   ├── auth.middleware.ts\n│   │   ├── role.middleware.ts\n│   │   ├── error.middleware.ts\n│   │   └── validate.middleware.ts\n│   │\n│   ├── validators/           # Request validation schemas\n│   │   ├── auth.validator.ts\n│   │   ├── student.validator.ts\n│   │   └── ...\n│   │\n│   ├── utils/                # Utilities\n│   │   ├── asyncHandler.ts\n│   │   ├── AppError.ts\n│   │   └── helpers.ts\n│   │\n│   ├── types/                # TypeScript types\n│   │   ├── index.ts\n│   │   └── express.d.ts\n│   │\n│   ├── constants/            # Constants\n│   │   ├── roles.ts\n│   │   └── status.ts\n│   │\n│   └── app.ts               # App entry point\n│\n├── tests/                    # Test files\n├── .env.example              # Environment template\n├── package.json\n└── tsconfig.json\n```\n\n### Database Connection\n\n```typescript\n// src/config/database.ts\nimport mongoose from 'mongoose';\n\nexport const connectDatabase = async () => {\n  try {\n    const mongoUri = process.env.MONGODB_URI || 'mongodb://localhost:27017/qlhv';\n    \n    await mongoose.connect(mongoUri);\n    \n    console.log('✅ MongoDB connected successfully');\n    \n    mongoose.connection.on('error', (err) => {\n      console.error('MongoDB connection error:', err);\n    });\n    \n    mongoose.connection.on('disconnected', () => {\n      console.warn('MongoDB disconnected');\n    });\n    \n  } catch (error) {\n    console.error('❌ MongoDB connection failed:', error);\n    process.exit(1);\n  }\n};\n```\n\n### Authentication Middleware\n\n```typescript\n// src/middlewares/auth.middleware.ts\nimport { FastifyRequest, FastifyReply } from 'fastify';\nimport jwt from 'jsonwebtoken';\n\nexport interface AuthUser {\n  id: string;\n  email: string;\n  role: 'admin' | 'teacher' | 'manager';\n}\n\nexport const authMiddleware = async (\n  request: FastifyRequest,\n  reply: FastifyReply\n) => {\n  try {\n    const token = request.headers.authorization?.replace('Bearer ', '');\n    \n    if (!token) {\n      return reply.status(401).send({\n        success: false,\n        message: 'Vui lòng đăng nhập'\n      });\n    }\n    \n    const decoded = jwt.verify(token, process.env.JWT_SECRET!) as AuthUser;\n    (request as any).user = decoded;\n    \n  } catch (error) {\n    return reply.status(401).send({\n      success: false,\n      message: 'Token không hợp lệ'\n    });\n  }\n};\n\nexport const roleMiddleware = (...roles: string[]) => {\n  return async (request: FastifyRequest, reply: FastifyReply) => {\n    const user = (request as any).user;\n    \n    if (!roles.includes(user.role)) {\n      return reply.status(403).send({\n        success: false,\n        message: 'Bạn không có quyền thực hiện hành động này'\n      });\n    }\n  };\n};\n```\n\n### API Response Format\n\n```typescript\n// Success Response\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": { ... },\n  \"message\": \"Thành công\"\n}\n\n// Error Response\n{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Lỗi\",\n  \"error\": {\n    \"code\": \"VALIDATION_ERROR\",\n    \"details\": [ ... ]\n  }\n}\n\n// Pagination Response\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"docs\": [ ... ],\n    \"meta\": {\n      \"totalItems\": 100,\n      \"itemCount\": 10,\n      \"itemsPerPage\": 10,\n      \"totalPages\": 10,\n      \"currentPage\": 1\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Frontend Documentation\n\n### Công nghệ sử dụng\n\n| Technology | Version | Purpose |\n|------------|---------|---------|\n| **React** | 18.x | UI library |\n| **Vite** | 5.x | Build tool |\n| **TypeScript** | 5.x | Type safety |\n| **React Router** | 6.x | Routing |\n| **TanStack Query** | 5.x | Data fetching |\n| **Zustand** | 4.x | State management |\n| **TailwindCSS** | 3.x | Styling |\n| **React Hook Form** | 7.x | Form handling |\n| **Zod** | - | Schema validation |\n\n### Cấu trúc thư mục\n\n```\nahv-dtlx-frontend/\n├── src/\n│   ├── api/                    # API clients\n│   │   ├── client.ts          # Axios instance\n│   │   ├── auth.api.ts        # Auth API\n│   │   ├── student.api.ts     # Student API\n│   │   ├── course.api.ts      # Course API\n│   │   ├── schedule.api.ts    # Schedule API\n│   │   ├── finance.api.ts     # Finance API\n│   │   └── report.api.ts      # Report API\n│   │\n│   ├── components/            # Reusable components\n│   │   ├── ui/               # Base components\n│   │   │   ├── Button.tsx\n│   │   │   ├── Input.tsx\n│   │   │   ├── Modal.tsx\n│   │   │   ├── Table.tsx\n│   │   │   ├── Select.tsx\n│   │   │   ├── DatePicker.tsx\n│   │   │   └── Loading.tsx\n│   │   │\n│   │   ├── layout/           # Layout components\n│   │   │   ├── Sidebar.tsx\n│   │   │   ├── Header.tsx\n│   │   │   ├── Footer.tsx\n│   │   │   └── PageLayout.tsx\n│   │   │\n│   │   ├── charts/           # Chart components\n│   │   │   ├── GrowthChart.tsx\n│   │   │   ├── PieChart.tsx\n│   │   │   └── StatCard.tsx\n│   │   │\n│   │   └── forms/            # Form components\n│   │       ├── StudentForm.tsx\n│   │       ├── CourseForm.tsx\n│   │       └── ...\n│   │\n│   ├── pages/                # Page components\n│   │   ├── Dashboard/\n│   │   ├── Students/\n│   │   ├── Courses/\n│   │   ├── Schedule/\n│   │   ├── Teachers/\n│   │   ├── Finance/\n│   │   ├── Reports/\n│   │   ├── Settings/\n│   │   └── Auth/\n│   │\n│   ├── hooks/               # Custom hooks\n│   │   ├── useAuth.ts\n│   │   ├── useStudents.ts\n│   │   ├── useCourses.ts\n│   │   └── ...\n│   │\n│   ├── contexts/            # React contexts\n│   │   ├── AuthContext.tsx\n│   │   └── ToastContext.tsx\n│   │\n│   ├── stores/              # Zustand stores\n│   │   ├── authStore.ts\n│   │   └── uiStore.ts\n│   │\n│   ├── routes/              # Route definitions\n│   │   ├── index.tsx\n│   │   ├── privateRoutes.tsx\n│   │   └── publicRoutes.tsx\n│   │\n│   ├── utils/               # Utilities\n│   │   ├── formatters.ts\n│   │   ├── validators.ts\n│   │   └── helpers.ts\n│   │\n│   ├── types/               # TypeScript types\n│   │   ├── api.types.ts\n│   │   ├── student.types.ts\n│   │   └── ...\n│   │\n│   ├── constants/           # Constants\n│   │   ├── routes.ts\n│   │   ├── roles.ts\n│   │   └── config.ts\n│   │\n│   ├── App.tsx\n│   └── main.tsx\n│\n├── public/\n├── index.html\n├── package.json\n├── tsconfig.json\n├── vite.config.ts\n└── tailwind.config.js\n```\n\n### API Client Configuration\n\n```typescript\n// src/api/client.ts\nimport axios from 'axios';\n\nconst API_BASE_URL = import.meta.env.VITE_API_URL || 'http://localhost:5555';\n\nexport const apiClient = axios.create({\n  baseURL: API_BASE_URL,\n  timeout: 30000,\n  headers: {\n    'Content-Type': 'application/json',\n  },\n});\n\n// Request interceptor\napiClient.interceptors.request.use(\n  (config) => {\n    const token = localStorage.getItem('token');\n    if (token) {\n      config.headers.Authorization = `Bearer ${token}`;\n    }\n    return config;\n  },\n  (error) => Promise.reject(error)\n);\n\n// Response interceptor\napiClient.interceptors.response.use(\n  (response) => response,\n  (error) => {\n    if (error.response?.status === 401) {\n      localStorage.removeItem('token');\n      window.location.href = '/login';\n    }\n    return Promise.reject(error);\n  }\n);\n```\n\n### State Management (Zustand)\n\n```typescript\n// src/stores/authStore.ts\nimport { create } from 'zustand';\nimport { persist } from 'zustand/middleware';\n\ninterface User {\n  id: string;\n  email: string;\n  name: string;\n  role: 'admin' | 'teacher' | 'manager';\n}\n\ninterface AuthState {\n  user: User | null;\n  token: string | null;\n  isAuthenticated: boolean;\n  \n  setAuth: (user: User, token: string) => void;\n  logout: () => void;\n  updateUser: (user: Partial<User>) => void;\n}\n\nexport const useAuthStore = create<AuthState>()(\n  persist(\n    (set) => ({\n      user: null,\n      token: null,\n      isAuthenticated: false,\n      \n      setAuth: (user, token) => set({ \n        user, \n        token, \n        isAuthenticated: true \n      }),\n      \n      logout: () => set({ \n        user: null, \n        token: null, \n        isAuthenticated: false \n      }),\n      \n      updateUser: (updates) => set((state) => ({\n        user: state.user ? { ...state.user, ...updates } : null\n      })),\n    }),\n    {\n      name: 'auth-storage',\n    }\n  )\n);\n```\n\n---\n\n## Coding Conventions\n\n### Backend Conventions\n\n#### 1. File Naming\n```\ncontroller → *.controller.ts\nservice → *.service.ts\nrepository → *.repository.ts\nmodel → *.model.ts\nroute → *.routes.ts\nmiddleware → *.middleware.ts\nvalidator → *.validator.ts\n```\n\n#### 2. Function Naming\n```typescript\n// Controllers: verbNoun\nasync function getStudents(req, res) {}\nasync function createStudent(req, res) {}\nasync function updateStudent(req, res) {}\nasync function deleteStudent(req, res) {}\n\n// Services: verbNoun\nasync function getStudentById(id) {}\nasync function createStudent(data) {}\nasync function updateStudent(id, data) {}\n\n// Repositories: findByXxx, create, update, delete\nasync function findById(id) {}\nasync function findAll(filter, options) {}\nasync function create(data) {}\n```\n\n#### 3. Error Handling\n```typescript\n// Always use asyncHandler wrapper\nexport const getStudent = asyncHandler(async (req, res) => {\n  const student = await studentService.getById(req.params.id);\n  \n  if (!student) {\n    throw new AppError('Không tìm thấy học viên', 404);\n  }\n  \n  res.success(student);\n});\n\n// AppError class\nexport class AppError extends Error {\n  constructor(\n    public message: string,\n    public statusCode: number = 500,\n    public code?: string\n  ) {\n    super(message);\n    this.name = 'AppError';\n  }\n}\n```\n\n#### 4. Response Format\n```typescript\n// Always use these helper methods\nres.success(data, message);\nres.created(data, message);\nres.error(message, statusCode);\nres.paginated(docs, meta);\n```\n\n### Frontend Conventions\n\n#### 1. Component Structure\n```typescript\n// 1. Imports\nimport React from 'react';\nimport { useState } from 'react';\nimport { Button } from '@/components/ui/Button';\nimport { useStudents } from '@/hooks/useStudents';\n\n// 2. Types\ninterface StudentCardProps {\n  student: Student;\n  onEdit: (id: string) => void;\n  onDelete: (id: string) => void;\n}\n\n// 3. Component\nexport const StudentCard: React.FC<StudentCardProps> = ({\n  student,\n  onEdit,\n  onDelete,\n}) => {\n  // 4. Hooks\n  const [isLoading, setIsLoading] = useState(false);\n  \n  // 5. Handlers\n  const handleDelete = async () => {\n    setIsLoading(true);\n    try {\n      await deleteStudent(student.id);\n    } finally {\n      setIsLoading(false);\n    }\n  };\n  \n  // 6. Render\n  return (\n    <div className=\"p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow\">\n      {/* JSX */}\n    </div>\n  );\n};\n```\n\n#### 2. Naming Conventions\n```typescript\n// Components: PascalCase\nStudentCard, DashboardPage, SidebarMenu\n\n// Hooks: camelCase with 'use' prefix\nuseStudents, useAuth, useFormSubmit\n\n// Functions: camelCase, verb prefix\nhandleSubmit, getStudentData, formatCurrency\n\n// Constants: SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE\nAPI_BASE_URL, MAX_FILE_SIZE, PAGE_SIZE\n\n// Types/Interfaces: PascalCase\ninterface StudentProps {}\ntype ApiResponse<T> = {}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Error Handling Strategy\n\n### Backend Error Handling\n\n```typescript\n// Error codes\nexport const ErrorCodes = {\n  // 400 - Bad Request\n  VALIDATION_ERROR: 'VALIDATION_ERROR',\n  INVALID_INPUT: 'INVALID_INPUT',\n  \n  // 401 - Unauthorized\n  UNAUTHORIZED: 'UNAUTHORIZED',\n  TOKEN_EXPIRED: 'TOKEN_EXPIRED',\n  TOKEN_INVALID: 'TOKEN_INVALID',\n  \n  // 403 - Forbidden\n  FORBIDDEN: 'FORBIDDEN',\n  \n  // 404 - Not Found\n  NOT_FOUND: 'NOT_FOUND',\n  USER_NOT_FOUND: 'USER_NOT_FOUND',\n  STUDENT_NOT_FOUND: 'STUDENT_NOT_FOUND',\n  \n  // 409 - Conflict\n  DUPLICATE_ENTRY: 'DUPLICATE_ENTRY',\n  \n  // 500 - Internal Server Error\n  INTERNAL_ERROR: 'INTERNAL_ERROR',\n  DATABASE_ERROR: 'DATABASE_ERROR',\n};\n\n// Global error handler middleware\nexport const errorHandler = (\n  error: Error,\n  request: FastifyRequest,\n  reply: FastifyReply\n) => {\n  if (error instanceof AppError) {\n    return reply.status(error.statusCode).send({\n      success: false,\n      message: error.message,\n      error: {\n        code: error.code,\n      },\n    });\n  }\n  \n  // Unexpected error\n  console.error('Unexpected error:', error);\n  \n  return reply.status(500).send({\n    success: false,\n    message: 'Đã xảy ra lỗi không mong muốn',\n    error: {\n      code: ErrorCodes.INTERNAL_ERROR,\n    },\n  });\n};\n```\n\n### Frontend Error Handling\n\n```typescript\n// Error boundaries\nexport class ErrorBoundary extends Component {\n  state = { hasError: false };\n  \n  static getDerivedStateFromError() {\n    return { hasError: true };\n  }\n  \n  componentDidCatch(error, errorInfo) {\n    console.error('Error:', error, errorInfo);\n  }\n  \n  render() {\n    if (this.state.hasError) {\n      return <ErrorFallback onRetry={() => this.setState({ hasError: false })} />;\n    }\n    return this.props.children;\n  }\n}\n\n// API error handling\ntry {\n  await apiClient.get('/students');\n} catch (error) {\n  if (error.response?.status === 404) {\n    showToast('Không tìm thấy dữ liệu', 'error');\n  } else if (error.response?.status === 401) {\n    showToast('Phiên đăng nhập hết hạn', 'warning');\n    navigate('/login');\n  } else {\n    showToast('Đã xảy ra lỗi', 'error');\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 📅 Cập nhật\n\n| Ngày | Phiên bản | Thay đổi |\n|------|-----------|-----------|\n| 2026-04-22 | 1.0 | Tạo mới tài liệu |\n","parent_id":"130744535"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":149,"output":4389,"cacheRead":23366,"cacheWrite":7679,"totalTokens":35583,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776837336207,"responseId":"063795d9de395a9e575f2023d2a71d0b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ab368c2c","parentId":"befadd2a","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:56:28.657Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_9k8av4to30rx_1","toolName":"confluence__create_page","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"id\":\"130842950\",\"title\":\"4. Tài liệu kỹ thuật - Technical Documentation\",\"space\":\"AHVTEACHER\",\"url\":\"https://dtlx.atlassian.net/spaces/AHVTEACHER/pages/130842950/4.+T+i+li+u+k+thu+t+-+Technical+Documentation\"}"}],"details":{"mcpServer":"confluence","mcpTool":"create_page"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776837388650}}
{"type":"message","id":"c4fc547a","parentId":"ab368c2c","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:57:15.501Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Tiếp tục tạo các trang còn lại. Đã có 4 trang rồi. Tiếp tục:\n- 5. API Documentation\n- 6. Database Documentation\n- 7. DevOps & Deployment\n- 8. Development Guideline\n- 9. Testing Documentation\n- 10. Operation & Maintenance","thinkingSignature":"cc63f8594103ff62b970835ac43aaaaf48cee6f781a0e673ac488fd0f34af0c1"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ti0v107ria4a_1","name":"confluence__create_page","arguments":{"title":"5. API Documentation - Auth & Student APIs","space":"AHVTEACHER","body":"# 5. API Documentation\n\n## 📋 Mục lục\n1. [API Overview](#api-overview)\n2. [Auth API](#auth-api)\n3. [Student API](#student-api)\n4. [Course API](#course-api)\n5. [Schedule API](#schedule-api)\n6. [Finance API](#finance-api)\n7. [Report API](#report-api)\n\n---\n\n## API Overview\n\n### Base URL\n```\nDevelopment: http://localhost:5555\nProduction:  https://api.qlhv.vn (chưa triển khai)\n```\n\n### Authentication\nTất cả API (trừ Auth) yêu cầu Bearer Token trong header:\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer <token>\n```\n\n### Response Format\n\n#### Success\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": { ... },\n  \"message\": \"Thành công\"\n}\n```\n\n#### Paginated Response\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"docs\": [ ... ],\n    \"meta\": {\n      \"totalItems\": 100,\n      \"itemCount\": 10,\n      \"itemsPerPage\": 10,\n      \"totalPages\": 10,\n      \"currentPage\": 1\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n#### Error\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Mô tả lỗi\",\n  \"error\": {\n    \"code\": \"ERROR_CODE\",\n    \"details\": [ ... ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### HTTP Status Codes\n| Code | Mô tả |\n|------|-------|\n| 200 | Thành công |\n| 201 | Đã tạo mới |\n| 400 | Bad Request - Lỗi validation |\n| 401 | Unauthorized - Chưa đăng nhập |\n| 403 | Forbidden - Không có quyền |\n| 404 | Not Found - Không tìm thấy |\n| 409 | Conflict - Trùng lặp dữ liệu |\n| 500 | Internal Server Error |\n\n---\n\n## Auth API\n\n### Base Path: `/auth`\n\n### 5.1.1. POST /auth/login - Đăng nhập\n\n**Request:**\n```json\n{\n  \"email\": \"teacher@qlhv.vn\",\n  \"password\": \"Password123\"\n}\n```\n\n**Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"token\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...\",\n    \"user\": {\n      \"id\": \"65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1\",\n      \"email\": \"teacher@qlhv.vn\",\n      \"name\": \"Nguyễn Văn A\",\n      \"role\": \"teacher\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"message\": \"Đăng nhập thành công\"\n}\n```\n\n**Error (401):**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Email hoặc mật khẩu không đúng\",\n  \"error\": { \"code\": \"UNAUTHORIZED\" }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5.1.2. POST /auth/register - Đăng ký (Admin only)\n\n**Request:**\n```json\n{\n  \"email\": \"newteacher@qlhv.vn\",\n  \"password\": \"Password123\",\n  \"name\": \"Trần Văn B\",\n  \"role\": \"teacher\"\n}\n```\n\n**Response (201):**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": \"65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d2\",\n    \"email\": \"newteacher@qlhv.vn\",\n    \"name\": \"Trần Văn B\",\n    \"role\": \"teacher\"\n  },\n  \"message\": \"Đăng ký thành công\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5.1.3. GET /auth/me - Lấy thông tin user hiện tại\n\n**Headers:**\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer <token>\n```\n\n**Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": \"65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1\",\n    \"email\": \"teacher@qlhv.vn\",\n    \"name\": \"Nguyễn Văn A\",\n    \"role\": \"teacher\",\n    \"teacherInfo\": {\n      \"phone\": \"0912345678\",\n      \"specialization\": \"B1, B2\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Student API\n\n### Base Path: `/students`\n\n### 5.2.1. GET /students - Danh sách học viên\n\n**Query Parameters:**\n| Parameter | Type | Default | Mô tả |\n|-----------|------|---------|-------|\n| page | number | 1 | Trang |\n| limit | number | 10 | Số item/trang |\n| search | string | - | Tìm kiếm theo tên/CCCD |\n| courseId | string | - | Lọc theo khóa học |\n| status | string | - | Lọc theo trạng thái |\n\n**Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"docs\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d3\",\n        \"name\": \"Lê Thị C\",\n        \"cccd\": \"012345678901\",\n        \"phone\": \"0987654321\",\n        \"dateOfBirth\": \"1995-03-15\",\n        \"address\": \"123 Đường ABC, TP.HCM\",\n        \"courses\": [\n          {\n            \"id\": \"65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d4\",\n            \"name\": \"Hạng B1 - Sáng\",\n            \"progress\": 75\n          }\n        ],\n        \"createdAt\": \"2026-01-15T10:30:00Z\"\n      }\n    ],\n    \"meta\": {\n      \"totalItems\": 150,\n      \"itemCount\": 10,\n      \"itemsPerPage\": 10,\n      \"totalPages\": 15,\n      \"currentPage\": 1\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5.2.2. GET /students/:id - Chi tiết học viên\n\n**Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": \"65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d3\",\n    \"name\": \"Lê Thị C\",\n    \"cccd\": \"012345678901\",\n    \"phone\": \"0987654321\",\n    \"dateOfBirth\": \"1995-03-15\",\n    \"address\": \"123 Đường ABC, TP.HCM\",\n    \"avatar\": \"https://storage.qlhv.vn/avatars/student-001.jpg\",\n    \"courses\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d4\",\n        \"name\": \"Hạng B1 - Sáng\",\n        \"code\": \"B1-S001\",\n        \"progress\": 75,\n        \"enrolledDate\": \"2026-01-15\",\n        \"status\": \"ongoing\"\n      }\n    ],\n    \"exams\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d5\",\n        \"type\": \"theory\",\n        \"score\": 85,\n        \"examDate\": \"2026-04-10\",\n        \"passed\": true\n      }\n    ],\n    \"createdAt\": \"2026-01-15T10:30:00Z\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5.2.3. POST /students - Tạo học viên mới\n\n**Request:**\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"Phạm Văn D\",\n  \"cccd\": \"012345678902\",\n  \"phone\": \"0971234567\",\n  \"dateOfBirth\": \"1998-07-20\",\n  \"address\": \"456 Đường XYZ, Hà Nội\",\n  \"email\": \"phamvand@email.com\"\n}\n```\n\n**Response (201):**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": \"65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d6\",\n    \"name\": \"Phạm Văn D\",\n    \"cccd\": \"012345678902\",\n    \"phone\": \"0971234567\",\n    \"dateOfBirth\": \"1998-07-20\",\n    \"address\": \"456 Đường XYZ, Hà Nội\",\n    \"email\": \"phamvand@email.com\",\n    \"status\": \"active\",\n    \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-22T05:55:00Z\"\n  },\n  \"message\": \"Tạo học viên thành công\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5.2.4. PUT /students/:id - Cập nhật học viên\n\n**Request:**\n```json\n{\n  \"phone\": \"0991234567\",\n  \"address\": \"789 Đường MNO, Đà Nẵng\"\n}\n```\n\n**Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": { ... },\n  \"message\": \"Cập nhật thành công\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5.2.5. DELETE /students/:id - Xóa học viên\n\n**Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Xóa học viên thành công\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5.2.6. POST /students/:id/enroll - Phân vào khóa học\n\n**Request:**\n```json\n{\n  \"courseId\": \"65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d4\"\n}\n```\n\n**Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"studentId\": \"65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d6\",\n    \"courseId\": \"65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d4\",\n    \"enrolledDate\": \"2026-04-22\",\n    \"progress\": 0\n  },\n  \"message\": \"Phân vào khóa học thành công\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Course API\n\n### Base Path: `/courses`\n\n### 5.3.1. GET /courses - Danh sách khóa học\n\n**Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"docs\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d4\",\n        \"code\": \"B1-S001\",\n        \"name\": \"Hạng B1 - Sáng\",\n        \"type\": \"B1\",\n        \"startDate\": \"2026-03-01\",\n        \"endDate\": \"2026-06-01\",\n        \"fee\": 5200000,\n        \"totalStudent\": 22,\n        \"maxStudent\": 30,\n        \"status\": \"ongoing\"\n      }\n    ],\n    \"meta\": { ... }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5.3.2. POST /courses - Tạo khóa học mới\n\n**Request:**\n```json\n{\n  \"code\": \"B2-T001\",\n  \"name\": \"Hạng B2 - Tối\",\n  \"type\": \"B2\",\n  \"startDate\": \"2026-05-01\",\n  \"endDate\": \"2026-08-01\",\n  \"fee\": 6000000,\n  \"maxStudent\": 30,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"days\": [\"Monday\", \"Wednesday\", \"Friday\"],\n    \"shift\": \"evening\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5.3.3. GET /courses/:id - Chi tiết khóa học (kèm danh sách học viên)\n\n**Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"id\": \"65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d4\",\n    \"code\": \"B1-S001\",\n    \"name\": \"Hạng B1 - Sáng\",\n    \"students\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d3\",\n        \"name\": \"Lê Thị C\",\n        \"cccd\": \"012345678901\",\n        \"progress\": 75,\n        \"status\": \"ongoing\"\n      }\n    ],\n    \"progress\": 45,\n    \"schedule\": { ... }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Schedule API\n\n### Base Path: `/schedules`\n\n### 5.4.1. GET /schedules - Danh sách lịch học\n\n**Query Parameters:**\n| Parameter | Type | Mô tả |\n|-----------|------|-------|\n| date | string | Ngày (YYYY-MM-DD) |\n| courseId | string | Lọc theo khóa học |\n| teacherId | string | Lọc theo giáo viên |\n| week | string | Tuần (YYYY-Www) |\n\n---\n\n### 5.4.2. POST /schedules - Tạo lịch học\n\n**Request:**\n```json\n{\n  \"courseId\": \"65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d4\",\n  \"teacherId\": \"65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1\",\n  \"date\": \"2026-04-25\",\n  \"shift\": \"morning\",\n  \"startTime\": \"08:00\",\n  \"endTime\": \"10:00\",\n  \"room\": \"P301\",\n  \"topic\": \"Đường đô thị - Kỹ năng quan sát\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Finance API\n\n### Base Path: `/finances`\n\n### 5.5.1. GET /finances - Danh sách giao dịch\n\n**Query Parameters:**\n| Parameter | Type | Mô tả |\n|-----------|------|-------|\n| type | string | \"in\" hoặc \"out\" |\n| category | string | Loại giao dịch |\n| startDate | string | Từ ngày |\n| endDate | string | Đến ngày |\n\n---\n\n### 5.5.2. POST /finances/revenue - Ghi nhận thu\n\n**Request:**\n```json\n{\n  \"amount\": 5200000,\n  \"description\": \"Thu học phí khóa B1-S001 - Lê Thị C\",\n  \"category\": \"tuition\",\n  \"studentId\": \"65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d3\",\n  \"courseId\": \"65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d4\",\n  \"paymentMethod\": \"cash\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5.5.3. POST /finances/expense - Ghi nhận chi\n\n**Request:**\n```json\n{\n  \"amount\": 500000,\n  \"description\": \"Mua nhiên liệu ô tô\",\n  \"category\": \"fuel\",\n  \"receipt\": \"https://storage.qlhv.vn/receipts/2026-04-001.jpg\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Report API\n\n### Base Path: `/reports`\n\n### 5.6.1. GET /reports/dashboard - Dashboard data\n\n**Response (200):**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"stats\": {\n      \"totalStudents\": 150,\n      \"activeCourses\": 12,\n      \"monthlyRevenue\": 52000000,\n      \"monthlyExpense\": 15000000\n    },\n    \"revenue\": [\n      { \"date\": \"2026-01\", \"data\": 45000000 },\n      { \"date\": \"2026-02\", \"data\": 52000000 },\n      { \"date\": \"2026-03\", \"data\": 48000000 }\n    ],\n    \"expense\": [\n      { \"date\": \"2026-01\", \"data\": 12000000 },\n      { \"date\": \"2026-02\", \"data\": 15000000 },\n      { \"date\": \"2026-03\", \"data\": 14000000 }\n    ],\n    \"recentTransactions\": [ ... ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5.6.2. GET /reports/export - Xuất báo cáo\n\n**Query Parameters:**\n| Parameter | Type | Mô tả |\n|-----------|------|-------|\n| type | string | \"revenue\", \"expense\", \"student\" |\n| format | string | \"pdf\", \"excel\" |\n| startDate | string | Từ ngày |\n| endDate | string | Đến ngày |\n\n---\n\n## 📅 Cập nhật\n\n| Ngày | Phiên bản | Thay đổi |\n|------|-----------|-----------|\n| 2026-04-22 | 1.0 | Tạo mới tài liệu |\n","parent_id":"130744535"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":151,"output":4130,"cacheRead":27727,"cacheWrite":7797,"totalTokens":39805,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776837388660,"responseId":"0637960d86e9b594bc5021613759c68a"}}
